//axhob_operation
{bust_privilege_regime_render}

NOTE: Prints the resolved field set for a single {burp_regime} profile
identified by a positional {burp_investiture} argument.
Read-only; no remote contact.

//axhopt_typed_parameter
{burp_investiture}

//axhoq_precondition
A {burp_regime} profile with the given {burp_investiture} exists in the
local station-user subtree.

//axhos_step
. *Locate profile*: resolve the profile file for the supplied
{burp_investiture} under the station-user subtree

//axhos_step
. *Resolve fields*: parse the profile and emit every defined
{burp_regime} field assignment

//axhog_guarantee
No remote network contact occurred and no field was modified on disk.

//axhoc_completion
Exit 0 on successful render.
Non-zero when the {burp_investiture} is not found or the profile fails
to parse.

//axhob_operation
{bust_node_regime_list}

NOTE: Lists every {burn_regime} profile in the project-global node
subtree without contacting any remote node.
Read-only enumeration; no station-user routing.

//axhoq_precondition
The node subtree at `.buk/rbmn_nodes/` exists and is readable by the
calling user.

//axhos_step
. *Enumerate local profiles*: scan the node subtree for {burn_regime}
profile files

//axhos_step
. *Display roster*: print each discovered {burn_viceroyalty}

//axhog_guarantee
No remote network contact occurred and no profile file was modified.

//axhoc_completion
Exit 0 on successful enumeration; an empty roster is success.
Non-zero only when the node subtree cannot be read.

//axhob_operation
{bust_privilege_regime_list}

NOTE: Lists every {burp_regime} profile in the local station-user subtree
without contacting any remote node.
Read-only enumeration scoped to the current {burs_user}.

//axhoq_precondition
The station-user subtree at `.buk/rbmu_users/{burs_user}/` exists and is
readable by the calling user.

//axhos_step
. *Enumerate local profiles*: scan the station-user subtree for
{burp_regime} profile files

//axhos_step
. *Display roster*: print each discovered {burp_investiture} for the
current {burs_user}

//axhog_guarantee
No remote network contact occurred and no profile file was modified.

//axhoc_completion
Exit 0 on successful enumeration; an empty roster is success.
Non-zero only when the station-user subtree cannot be read.

//axhob_operation
{bust_node_regime_render}

NOTE: Prints the resolved field set for a single {burn_regime} profile
identified by a positional {burn_viceroyalty} argument.
Read-only; no remote contact.

//axhopt_typed_parameter
{burn_viceroyalty}

//axhoq_precondition
A {burn_regime} profile with the given {burn_viceroyalty} exists in the
local node subtree.

//axhos_step
. *Locate profile*: resolve the profile file for the supplied
{burn_viceroyalty} under the node subtree

//axhos_step
. *Resolve fields*: parse the profile and emit every defined
{burn_regime} field assignment

//axhog_guarantee
No remote network contact occurred and no field was modified on disk.

//axhoc_completion
Exit 0 on successful render.
Non-zero when the {burn_viceroyalty} is not found or the profile fails
to parse.

//axhob_operation
{bust_node_regime_validate}

NOTE: Validates a single {burn_regime} profile, identified by positional
{burn_viceroyalty}, for required-field presence and {burn_platform} enum
conformance.
Read-only; no remote contact.

//axhopt_typed_parameter
{burn_viceroyalty}

//axhoq_precondition
A {burn_regime} profile with the given {burn_viceroyalty} exists in the
local node subtree.

//axhos_step
. *Load profile*: parse the profile file for the supplied
{burn_viceroyalty}

//axhos_step
. *Required fields*: confirm {burn_host} and {burn_platform} are present

//axhos_step
. *Platform sanity*: confirm {burn_platform} is exactly one of
`linux | mac | cygwin | wsl | powershell | localhost`

//axhog_guarantee
The verdict reflects the on-disk state at call time; no field was
modified.

//axhoc_completion
Exit 0 when every check passes.
Non-zero with a diagnostic message identifying the first failed check.

//axhob_operation
{bust_privilege_regime_validate}

NOTE: Validates a single {burp_regime} profile, identified by positional
{burp_investiture}, for required-field presence and field-type
conformance.
Read-only; no remote contact.

//axhopt_typed_parameter
{burp_investiture}

//axhoq_precondition
A {burp_regime} profile with the given {burp_investiture} exists in the
local station-user subtree.

//axhos_step
. *Load profile*: parse the profile file for the supplied
{burp_investiture}

//axhos_step
. *Required fields*: confirm {burp_node}, {burp_user}, and
{burp_ssh_pubkey} are present

//axhos_step
. *Optional fields*: confirm {burp_key_file} and {burp_command} either
parse cleanly as their declared types or are explicitly empty

//axhog_guarantee
The verdict reflects the on-disk state at call time; no field was
modified.

//axhoc_completion
Exit 0 when every check passes.
Non-zero with a diagnostic message identifying the first failed check.

